{"tid":1227583,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我係澳門人 但我聽日都會去遊行","createTime":"2019-06-15T15:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T04:48:09.000Z","uid":113854,"like":145,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ffe17bdcd2c7480bc33bbdaa7ab63100786b98b4","tid":1227583,"uid":113854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:18:55.000Z","msg":"寫緊呢篇文嘅時候我搭緊船黎香港，準備發夢聽日同大家一齊遊行。<br />\n<br />\n其實除左我之外都仲有好多澳門人關心緊香港。我知道香港人同澳門人喺網上成日有罵戰，但當中有唔少係3毛搞分化。始終澳門同香港一樣，都係一國兩制，如果聯合起黎對抗中共咪話唔驚！所以啲3毛得閒就話下香港人淨係識投訴，又得閒話下澳門人淨係識收錢，結果大家就會跟風去鬧，好似長輩圖咁。<br />\n<br />\n我自幼喺澳門生活，澳門維穩真係做得太好。從小教育都好少講關於政治嘅議題，大部分澳門人淨係睇cctvb了解時事。仲記得每次播到香港遊行示威/集會，我呀媽淨係識講一句: 啲人成日搞搞震。大家都知cctvb嘅報導係幾識隱瞞同幾有誤導性架啦，結果大部分澳門人喺唔了解成件事嘅情況下就下左定論。甚至唔只cctvb，仲有澳門日報。唔知大家記唔記得當年澳門反離補法案有2萬人上街遊行，喺蘋果上左頭條，但澳門日報嘅頭版竟然係賣汽車廣告，到依家我都仲係印象深刻。所以大部分澳門人親中無可避免，佢地根本唔會接收到中共負面嘅一面，希望大家可以體諒下，唔好因爲咁而敵視澳門人。我都試過去說服我屋企人，但有啲根深蒂固嘅觀念唔係一時三刻改變到，我都好有無力感。值得慶幸嘅係我呀爸雖然勸我唔好去，但都無阻止到我黎香港。<br />\n<br />\n幾年前我黎到香港讀書，發現又係另一個世界。大家好不畏強權咁去發聲，甚至佔領中環，其實對當時嘅我黎講係好震撼。當時我有幫手庇護同跟住去送物資，呢啲凝聚力係只有喺現場先感受得到，亦令我覺得好感動。雖然我依家都唔係特別關心政治，但我覺得已經比以前進步，至少我肯出黎示威。<br />\n<br />\n大家真係要好好珍惜依家仲擁有自由嘅香港，一旦通過逃犯條例，大家漸漸唔會敢發聲，香港到時會慢慢被大陸同化，然後想再發聲都會被滅聲。Facebook, IG, Youtube, Google, Line等等，都會被限制。然後，就沒有然後了。所以我地聽日一定要出黎，人數至少唔好少過上次，先表達到民眾逐漸增強嘅怨念。<br />\n<br />\n喺今日有人為對抗送中而犧牲自己，如果你地稍微有啲血性，都應該知道自己要點做先唔好令佢白白犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n我都出黎行，你呢？聽日約定你地，香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7ea9a088fa3c0538b71cc8d920fb9ea6d27a96","tid":1227583,"uid":113854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:21:51.000Z","msg":"推到大家聽日都出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb793a10e0b37cfc5df8433c75666f44dc45154d","tid":1227583,"uid":113854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:22:50.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1e06fd757c0e122a32da72c59a4b6423228388","tid":1227583,"uid":113854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:24:58.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8434f1171adfc21c9e0149385730b487dc80c16","tid":1227583,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"ddb1ecdeb6330fc290e512d0d8336e01a8c0b21e","tid":1227583,"uid":113854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"為左今日個犧牲者 聽日出黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fc49b6c2144e05cb5a463044b07fbdc73928c1","tid":1227583,"uid":113854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:32:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57ed7725c08f0742477de213db0087c434c3483","tid":1227583,"uid":113854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339db6df061f96e672b5c5abe9147ebd83e8f747","tid":1227583,"uid":113854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T15:55:52.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以用少少時間睇一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b651d6e714ebf9250c80ef7400c828b79a91f3","tid":1227583,"uid":113854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:02:10.000Z","msg":"繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c8426ee5cb28191b258c417ff8b8e1685bd031","tid":1227583,"uid":70411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:05:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府團結左全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ab80a4a9a4ee8290fd3a2ee17f0d9e635e0cf4","tid":1227583,"uid":231691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:05:45.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc66322519f12fccbc8df5b7fb0038872a7d2340","tid":1227583,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6a9aee5b8860fcc263fc4ca8d23b66437432a3c","tid":1227583,"uid":113854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:11:37.000Z","msg":"不撤不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a733e17f59e2777631527c1eff9f6e048e9dfb","tid":1227583,"uid":82853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:11:59.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日見"},{"pid":"5c01ec628258463863bb1d9de8bf30d8438a5123","tid":1227583,"uid":116360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e330a89bdc0a89480ba26859bc46c3efe5156d25","tid":1227583,"uid":157678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:17:06.000Z","msg":"澳門人表示支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f93e471c303e3f8ea44a65ab230e1759f18d18a","tid":1227583,"uid":37430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"澳門人表示支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係海外入左文宣部"},{"pid":"b88eec82ddb56a943f78db938bfbd72aacd7a645","tid":1227583,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dis